{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_05_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 思い出を巡れば",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ二日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――2 days before the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1420.0000048000002,
          "startTime": 1.4200000048
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こんばんは、莉央さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 4.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、貴方まだいたの？　相変わらず仕事の虫ね\n少しは休まないと体に悪いわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you're still here? You're as much of a workaholic as ever. You really should take a break.\nWorking without a break is bad for your health.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、莉央さんが忘れ物を取りに事務所に来るって\n葵から聞いたので、待っていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I heard from Aoi that you were coming to the office to pick up something‚ Rio-san.\nSo‚ I was waiting for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "待っていた？　もしかして次のライブのこと？\n何か問題でもあったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waiting for me? Is it about the next live?\nIs there some sort of problem?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、琴乃から聞いてます。莉央さんが\n『星の海の記憶』を歌うことに躊躇してるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Kotono. She mentioned that you were hesitating about\nsinging \"Memories of the Starry Sky\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その話\nそれなら、さっき琴乃にも言ったけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that topic.\nWell‚ I told Kotono earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい！\n結論を出す前に俺の話を聞いてくれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait!\nBefore you make a decision‚ would you listen to what I have to say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　結論なら、琴乃と話してもう出てるんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㄷh? Well‚ the decision has already been made after I talked to Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、話だけでも！　どうかお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ just the conversation‚ please! Could you hear me out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かったわよ！　聞くから\n……もう、近いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine! I'm listening.\n…You are too close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんが歌わない、という気持ちも理解出来ます\nでも……俺は、それでも歌うべきだと思うんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand the feeling behind your decision not to sing‚ Rio-san.\nBut… I believe you should sing anyway!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "――はい？\nそうね……だから私は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――What?\nWell‚ yes… So‚ I was saying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈も莉央さんなら、納得してくれると思うんです\nだから、麻奈のためにも歌ってほしいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think even Mana would agree if it's you‚ Rio-san.\nThat's why‚ for Mana's sake‚ I want you to sing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8343333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "え……ええ、琴乃も同じことを言っていたわ\nだから、さっき彼女と話して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Well‚ Kotono said something similar earlier…\nSo‚ I talked to her about it‚ and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、もう一度俺の話を聞いて、考え直して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ just listen to me one more time and reconsider…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　なんなの！？\nそういう貴方こそ、私の話聞いてる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh! What's gotten into you!?\nAren't YOU supposed to be listening to me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さんは怒ってるが、ひるんじゃダメだ……）\n（琴乃達のため、そして莉央さん自身のためにも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rio-san seems angry‚ but I can't back down now…）\n（For Kotono and Mana‚ and for Rio-san herself…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.968343292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……さては、勘違いしてるわね\nねえ、貴方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can tell you've misunderstood something.\nHey‚ you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私に、そこまで麻奈の曲を歌わせたいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you want me to sing Mana's song so badly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません、うまく説明するのは難しいんですけど\n莉央さんはそうすべきだって、思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry‚ it's hard to explain properly.\nBut I just think you should do it‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "私のためを思って、そう言っている\nそういうことね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're saying this for my sake‚ right?\nIs that it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん。いいでしょう。考えてあげてもいいわ\nただし条件がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahem. Fine‚ I'll consider it.\nBut I have a condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の曲を本気で歌うなら\nもっと彼女のことを深く理解する必要があるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I am seriously going to sing Mana's song‚\nI need to understand her much better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "彼女のこと、私に詳しく教えなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me everything you know about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺の知っていることならなんでも説明します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll explain anything I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
