      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、星見市であの子と一緒に過ごしてたんでしょ？\nその思い出の場所によ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You spent time with that girl in Hoshimi City‚ didn't you?\nTake me to the place of those memories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら、少しは考えてあげてもいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you do that‚ then I might consider it a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。それで考えてくれるならいくらでも\nお供します。さっそく、明日行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. If you'll think about it‚ I'll go anywhere you want.\nLet's go tomorrow then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "本当はもう決めてるんだけど……\n面白そうだから、しばらく黙ってましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've actually already made up my mind…\nBut since it sounds interesting‚ let's keep it a secret for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "何か言いました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you say something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
