      "text": "何しろ時間がなかったので……。打ち合わせ中でも\n移動中でもアイデアが浮かんだらすぐ書き留めてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we were really short on time… Even during our meetings‚\nor while we were on the move‚ if an idea came up‚ she'd jot it down immediately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 202.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "ステージの外でも随分と自由奔放だったのね\n真面目な琴乃とは随分違うわ。意外ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So she was quite carefree even off the stage.\nQuite different from the serious Kotono. Surprising.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーとしては琴乃みたいな子の方がずっと\nやりやすいですよ。何度あいつの無茶に振り回されたか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a manager‚ dealing with girls like Kotono is much easier.\nYou have no idea how many times I've been dragged along by her reckless ideas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、麻奈のことを話している今の貴方は\nとても楽しそうだけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But right now‚ as you talk about Mana‚\nYou seem to be having a lot of fun‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
