        "en": "It's just that when you talk about Mana‚ your true face comes out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、よく分かったわ\nやっぱり麻奈は特別なのね。貴方にとっても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I understand now.\nMana is special after all. And that goes for you too.",
        "id": ""
